            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">You have 200 designs across t-shirts, hoodies, mugs, phone cases. Customer orders 3 items, each from different products. Without automation: you manually send orders to printer, chase shipping updates, pray nothing gets mixed up. With Shopify + Printful: customer orders â†’ printer notified â†’ shipping to customer â†’ tracking updated automatically. You designed once, sell forever. POD = design once, sell infinitely. Automation required. Otherwise you're an order clerk, not a designer.</p>
