        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">01</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Built working POD stores with real products</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Created full POD stores with 50-100 products each. Integrated Printful, tested mockup generators, set up auto-fulfillment. Measured order processing time from purchase to printer notification. Didn't just test featuresâ€”built working POD operations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">02</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Tested mobile impulse buying behavior</p>
