            <li><strong>Month 3:</strong> Jake now designs 6 hours daily instead of 4 (2.5 hours saved from order processing). Added 150 new designs (450 new products). Total: 350 designs, 1,200 products. Orders: 40-60 daily. Revenue: $7,800 (+50% from month 2). Net profit after fees: $4,800/month. 90-day total: $16,400 revenue vs. $5,400 previous quarter. Growth: 204%</li>
