            <strong>The brutal truth:</strong> POD at scale requires automation. 10 orders/day with manual processing = manageable. 100 orders/day manual = impossible. Shopify + Printful: 10 or 10,000 orders, same effort. You designed once, should sell infinitely. Every order requiring human intervention defeats POD's promise. Automation isn't luxuryâ€”it's survival at scale.
          </p>
